# Mirror the repo-root .kota/ ignore so a workflow's tmpdir-git inside this
# fixture sees realistic gitignore behavior (run artifacts under .kota/runs/
# stay untracked, matching production). The explorer-state file is the only
# .kota/ entry the fixture seeds, and the explorer writes through it during
# the run; keep it tracked via selective re-inclusion so the initial commit
# captures it and later rewrites land as diffs against HEAD.
.kota/*
!.kota/explorer-state.json
node_modules/
